column4: CORRECTED-US STOCKS-U.S. stocks fall  with retail  technology leading rout
column5: Nov 13 U.S. stock indexes fell sharply on Friday  weighed down by consumer retail and technology stocks after disappointing forecasts from Cisco and department store chains suggested weakening demand heading into the key holiday shopping season.
